Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.38,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Ronaldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.38,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,ロナルド
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.65,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Bring my brother back to the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.65,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,兄さんをファミリーに戻してあげて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:13.88,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ネロがガラッシアに忠誠を誓えば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:15.80,Default,ron,0,0,0,,If Nero swears loyalty to the Galassias, I'll let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:15.80,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,命だけは助けてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:20.32,Default,ron,0,0,0,,However Frate's the next don and down the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:20.32,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,が 次のドンはフラテだ そしてゆくゆくは...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:24.90,Default,fio,0,0,0,,I just don't want to see our family fighting anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:24.90,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,家族で争うのだけはもう見たくないの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:26.98,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:26.98,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.86,Default,ron,0,0,0,,It's all up to Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.86,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,すべてはネロ次第だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.16,Default,ron,0,0,0,,If he submits...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.16,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,奴は跪くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:47.03,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}kanjou ni tsukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:47.03,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}I can assign whatever name I wish
