Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:01.42,OP_Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}tsumi no hikigane ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:01.42,OP_English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}My unrepentable sins
