Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:17.04,Default,fan,0,0,0,,The trick to squeezing a lemon is to roll it in your hands for thirty seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:17.04,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,しぼる骨はレモンを30秒を転がしてやるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:19.36,Default,fan,0,0,0,,exerting just a little pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:19.36,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,少し力を入れてな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:22.10,Default,fan,0,0,0,,That'll make it less bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:22.10,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,そうすると 苦味が減る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:24.02,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Now it's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:24.02,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,これで完璧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.91,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Go on, eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.91,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,さ 食ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.99,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I want to thank you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.99,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,今日はお前たちを労いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.96,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We gladly accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.96,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,遠慮なくいただくぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.96,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I really am grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.96,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,本当に感謝してるんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.13,Default,fan,0,0,0,,you took care of Orco.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.13,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,オルコを片付けられたんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.99,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.99,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,お陰で 俺は今や
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.64,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I'm the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.64,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,キングだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.11,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The flavor's about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.11,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,味は落ちてねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:46.93,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.80,Default,lac,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.80,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,ねね そう言えば知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:55.43,Default,lac,0,0,0,,This cheese was imported from Puglia in southern Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:55.43,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,このチーズ 南イタリアのプーリアから取り寄せたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.81,Default,lac,0,0,0,,You know Puglia? It's in the heel of the boot,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.81,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,知ってるかしら イタリアの踵のところ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:02.23,Default,lac,0,0,0,,and it was a relative of Rudolph Valentino's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:02.23,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,でね ルドルフ バレンティノと親戚だったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.58,Default,lac,0,0,0,,You can see the resemblance in the eyes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.58,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,目元とか似てない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.98,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,この人のママも澄み切ったアドリア海みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:10.00,Default,lac,0,0,0,,His mama had that color, too.\N Like the Adriatic Sea, so pure—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.82,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,とっても純粋な
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.42,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Now we take out the Vanetti family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.42,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,後はバネッチィ ファミリーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.09,Default,fan,0,0,0,,We're a team now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:20.96,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,俺達は仲間だ 生きてる限りの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.88,Default,fan,0,0,0,,As long as we live...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.80,Default,nero,0,0,0,,More like roommates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.80,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,それを言うなら ルームメイトだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.68,Default,nero,0,0,0,,As long as I'm renting a room from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.68,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,部屋を借りてる限り
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:27.57,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:29.65,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Either way, I want you to—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:29.65,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,どっちにしろ 存分...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.83,Overlap,lac,0,0,0,,I want you to go out and make trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.83,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,{\an8}存分に暴れて頂戴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.06,Default,lac,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.06,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,期待してるは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.94,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Well, wouldn't want to let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.94,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,じゃ 期待に応えなきゃな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:42.33,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Don't you want your drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:42.33,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,もう酒はいいのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.24,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Nah, I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.24,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あ 十分だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:49.59,Default,fan,0,0,0,,That's right! You've got some\N pretty great booze, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:49.59,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,そうだよな お前ら 随分に酒持ってんだもんな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:54.06,Default,lac,0,0,0,,Hey, let me have some next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:54.06,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,ね 今度 飲ませて頂戴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.05,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That damn Fango.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.05,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファンゴの野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:04.13,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He's gonna run us ragged,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:04.13,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺達を俺達を徹底的に使い倒す気でいやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:07.02,Default,av,0,0,0,,and he'll try to steal Lawless Heaven from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:07.02,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,このままじゃ ローレス ヘブンもとられる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.74,Default,av,0,0,0,,Then, once we're no longer useful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.74,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,そして 用が済んだら...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.28,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What do you advise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.28,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お前なら どうする
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:21.51,Default,av,0,0,0,,In the end, the Vanetti family is the only place we can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:21.51,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,結局 安息の地はバネッチィ ファミリーにしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.46,Default,av,0,0,0,,The problem is Frate and Ronaldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.46,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,問題はフラテとロナルドだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.84,Default,ron,0,0,0,,What an awful state...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.84,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,酷いな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.75,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.75,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,おいおい どうしたシーザー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.41,Default,ron,0,0,0,,You looked so bold when you were casting the die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.41,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,賽を投げた時は勇ましかったのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.55,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Seems a little late for regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.55,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,今更後悔か?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:47.00,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Frate, you have some good points that Nero lacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:47.00,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,フラテ お前にはネロにない いいところがある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.39,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.39,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,どんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.76,Default,ron,0,0,0,,You're sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.76,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,素直なとことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.56,Default,ron,0,0,0,,That's what I first liked about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.56,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,俺が気に入ったのはそこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:57.98,Default,ron,0,0,0,,You're the only one who really\N worries about the family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:57.98,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,本当にファミリーを心配してるのはお前だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.50,Default,ron,0,0,0,,So you need to kill Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.50,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,なら ネロをやるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.02,Default,ron,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can save the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.02,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ファミリーを救えるのは お前しかいない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:08.86,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Take this and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:08.86,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,これを飲んで ゆっくり休め
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.94,Default,man,0,0,0,,Lawless Heaven, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.94,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,ローレス ヘブンをくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:22.12,Default,man,0,0,0,,I just hit the jackpot! Gimme a whole bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:22.12,720通用注釋-ja,man,0,0,0,,バカづき:打麻雀用語,意思是行大運.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:22.12,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,今日は バカづきしたからよ ボトルでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.26,Default,bar,0,0,0,,If you want to drink that, go to one of Fango's bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.26,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,あの酒が飲みたきゃ ファンゴの店に行け
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:26.98,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,逆だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:29.48,Default,man,0,0,0,,That's backwards, ain't it?\N Vanetti bars are the only ones that deal in—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:30.22,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,ありゃ バネッチィの店でしか扱ってないんじゃなかっ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.20,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:38.88,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,暫くの間でいい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:41.36,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Why not buy from Fango just for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.36,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファンゴんとこから仕入れてくれねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.29,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We'll do you right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.29,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,悪いようにはしねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:50.02,Default,bar,0,0,0,,All right, but you'll owe me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:50.02,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,分かりました 一つ貸しにしときますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.77,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That's the way. I'm in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.77,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そうこなくっちゃ 恩に着るぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.91,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Hey, you boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.91,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,おい お前ら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.62,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Stop making trouble on our turf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.62,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,勝手にシマを荒らすんじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.30,Default,vol,0,0,0,,We've got nothing to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.30,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,あんたとは遣り合いたくねい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.04,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Turn around and head back out that—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.58,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,回れ右して 早速帰れ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.15,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey there, Uncle Ganzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.15,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ガンゾの叔父貴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:12.38,Default,gan,0,0,0,,How's the food at Fango's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:12.38,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ファンゴの飯は旨いか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.43,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.98,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Of course, we don't eat free.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.98,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,勿論 ただ飯って訳にはいかねぇけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.54,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Could I speak to you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.54,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ちょっと面貸せ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:27.00,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Come home, Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:27.00,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,戻ってこい ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.54,Default,gan,0,0,0,,It's just a feud between brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.54,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ただの兄弟喧嘩だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:31.70,Default,gan,0,0,0,,I'll mediate on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:31.70,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,俺が話しをつけてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:37.46,Default,gan,0,0,0,,I taught you and Frate both about women.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:37.46,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,お前もフラテも 俺が女を教えてやった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.87,Default,gan,0,0,0,,I made you into a real man,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.87,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,一人前の男にしてやったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.17,Default,gan,0,0,0,,so shut up and do as I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.17,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,黙って言うことを聞けい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.64,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That sure was a rough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.64,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あれは酷かった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:50.65,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Lots of people in the family miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:50.65,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ファミリーにはお前を慕ってるやつが多い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.38,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.38,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どうだかな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:55.59,Default,gan,0,0,0,,It's true. They all wanted to be the one to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:55.59,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,本当だ 皆遣りたかってるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:56.88,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:56.88,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ったく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:59.74,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I can't argue with you, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:59.74,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,叔父きには敵わねねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.10,Default,fra,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.10,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,んだよこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.46,Default,fra,0,0,0,,What are those accountants doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.46,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,会計士は何をしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.29,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Profits are half what they were three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.29,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,上がりが三か月前の半分だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:12.23,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Nero took the secret brewery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:12.23,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,密造酒はネロが持っていった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:13.98,Default,gan,0,0,0,,To make money bootlegging—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:13.98,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ブーツレッグで稼ぐには...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.74,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you naïve?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.74,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,呑気なもんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.52,Default,gan,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.52,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,何だと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.74,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Even after you met with him, Nero's kept making trouble on our turf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.74,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,あなたが会った後も ネロはうちのシマを荒らしてます
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:26.04,Default,ron,0,0,0,,At this rate, Fango and Nero are\N going to drive us out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:26.04,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,このままだとファンゴとネロに潰されますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.76,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Right now, it's life or death between Nero and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.76,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,もう 兄さんとは生きるか死ぬかなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:35.14,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Are you gonna say that in front of Vincent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:35.14,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,お前 そのセリフをヴィンセントの前で吐けるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.72,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Let me use this chance to make things clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.72,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,この際だ はっきりさせておきましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.46,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Nero is the enemy of the family,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.46,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ネロはファミリーの敵です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:50.58,Default,ron,0,0,0,,and Don Galassia wants Frate to take over the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:50.58,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ドン ガラッシアもフラテが後を継ぐことを希望していますしね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.23,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What's Fango doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.23,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファンゴの動きがどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.60,Default,av,0,0,0,,He probably already knows where the Lodge is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.60,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ロッチの場所はもう知られてるだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.58,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あんなもん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:04.16,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Who cares? Without the recipe, it's just a big steam bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:04.16,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,酒のレシピがなけりゃ ただのでっかい蒸し風呂だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:07.38,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Which means it's Corteo we need to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:07.38,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,となると コルテオが心配だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:10.68,Default,av,0,0,0,,He'll be fine. Barbero is with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:10.68,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,大丈夫 バルベロがついてくれてる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.52,Default,fio,0,0,0,,It's onion soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.52,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,オニオンスープよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.73,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I remember. Mama Connie\N used to make it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.73,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,コニー母さんがよく作ってくれたっけな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:49.40,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Can't we go back to the way things were?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:49.40,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,もう一度 昔みたいになれないの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:52.83,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I've always supported Dad to protect the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:52.83,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺はファミリーを守るために親父を支えてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.42,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I plan to keep doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.42,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,これからもそうするつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.72,Default,fra,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.72,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,違うだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.86,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,兄さんが考えてるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:09:01.17,Default,fra,0,0,0,,All you're thinking about is your cheap pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:01.17,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,薄っぺらいプライドのことだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:03.42,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,プライドをなくしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:05.94,Default,nero,0,0,0,,There's no point in protecting the \Nfamily if we don't have our pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.02,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファミリーを守る意味すらなくなっちまうだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.13,Default,fra,0,0,0,,If we go against the Galassias, the family will be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:09.11,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,ガラッシアに逆らったら ファミリーは潰されるんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.96,Default,fra,0,0,0,,We'll lose everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.96,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,元も子もないじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:14.56,Default,nero,0,0,0,,So you want to let the Vanettis\N be swallowed up by the Galassias?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:14.56,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ガラッシアはバネッチィを飲み込んじまうつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.58,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Our only choice is to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.58,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,戦うしかねんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.69,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Why can't you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.69,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なんで分からねんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:23.10,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Fio married Ronaldo to keep that from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:23.10,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,そうならない為に 姉さんはロナルドと結婚した
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.24,Default,fra,0,0,0,,But you ruined—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.24,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,なのに 兄さんがめちくちゃ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:28.07,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You're Ronaldo's puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:28.07,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お前はロナルドの操る人形なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.13,Default,fra,0,0,0,,You always... always, always...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.13,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,いつも いつも いつも...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.34,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Ever since we were children,\N you just did whatever you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.34,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,兄さんは子供の頃からやりたいことだけやってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.76,Default,fra,0,0,0,,You never went to Sunday mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.76,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,日曜の礼拝にも行かないで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.74,Default,fra,0,0,0,,You played around however you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.74,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,好き勝手に遊んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:48.06,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I invited you, but you never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:48.06,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お前は誘っても来なかったよな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.51,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You were scared of Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.51,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,いつも親父を怖がってた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:54.93,Default,fra,0,0,0,,You've always looked down on me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:54.93,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,兄さんはそうやって いつも俺を見下してきたん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.17,Default,nero,0,0,0,,But Ronaldo is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.17,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,だけど ロナルドが違う
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.86,Default,fra,0,0,0,,He acknowledges me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.86,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,俺を認めてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.83,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Power's not something you have acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.83,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,力は認めてもらうもんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.33,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You prove it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.33,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,自分で示すもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.13,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Don't talk down to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.13,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,そんなこと言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.90,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,自分のわがままで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:11.79,Default,fra,0,0,0,,It's your selfishness that ruined our family!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.79,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,ファミリーをむちゃくちゃしてやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:14.91,Default,fra,0,0,0,,If you'd just die, our family would go back to—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:14.91,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,お前さえ死ねば ファミリーは元通り
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.69,Default,fio,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.69,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,いい加減にして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.77,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Brother, please, talk to Ronaldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.77,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,兄さん ロナルドと話し合って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:30.76,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Maybe the Galassias would take this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:30.76,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,もしかしたら この町はガラッシアに取られるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.45,Default,fio,0,0,0,,But our family would go back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.45,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,でも 家族は元に戻るわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.16,Default,fio,0,0,0,,You're both the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.16,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,あんた達は2人とも同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:42.21,Default,fio,0,0,0,,What "family" are you even talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:42.21,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,あんた達の言ってる「ファミリー」っては何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.66,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Brothers killing each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.66,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,兄弟で殺し合って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.41,Default,fio,0,0,0,,What kind of family is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.41,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,何がファミリーよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:49.14,Default,fio,0,0,0,,I don't care about that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:49.14,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,そんなのどうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:54.36,Default,fio,0,0,0,,I just don't want to see brothers...\Nto see family killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:54.36,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,兄弟で家族で殺し合うことだけはやめて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:56.70,Default,fio,0,0,0,,No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:56.70,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,絶対に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.30,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's gotten cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.30,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,冷めちまったなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.50,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'll work things out with Ronaldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.50,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ロナルドと話をつける
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:17.93,Default,av,0,0,0,,Did the reunion make you nostalgic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:17.93,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,久々の再会で里心がついたのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:21.47,Default,av,0,0,0,,Throw off the cheap sentimentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:21.47,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,安い感傷捨てろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:24.12,Default,av,0,0,0,,With Frate, it's kill or be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:24.12,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,フラテとはやるかやられるかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:27.07,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He's still my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:27.07,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あいつは血を分けた兄弟だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.49,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Family's more important than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.49,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なりよりも大切な家族なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.03,Default,av,0,0,0,,I had a little brother like him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.03,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,俺にもそん弟がいた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:37.51,Default,av,0,0,0,,I'll let you meet him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:37.51,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,そのうちに合わせてやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.55,Default,av,0,0,0,,Nero's going to die if this keeps up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.55,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,このままだと ネロは死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.49,Default,vol,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.49,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,何の話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:50.37,Default,av,0,0,0,,Nero says he's going to work things out with Ronaldo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:50.37,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ネロはロナルドと話をつけると言ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.31,Default,av,0,0,0,,but things have gone too far for that to work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.31,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,だけど もうそんな状況じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:57.92,Default,av,0,0,0,,You saved Nero back at the Vanetti mansion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:57.92,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,前にヴァネッティの屋敷でもネロを助けてくれたかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:11:59.48,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.99,Default,av,0,0,0,,I need your help again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.99,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,もう一度力を貸してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.90,Default,vol,0,0,0,,I'd do anything for Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.90,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,ネロのためなら何だってやる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:10.40,Default,av,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's Sunday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:10.40,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,明日は日曜日だったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:21.79,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Every week like clockwork, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:21.79,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,毎週 律儀なことだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:25.24,Default,fra,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:25.24,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,別に付き合ってくれとは言ったねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.57,Default,ron,0,0,0,,I heard from Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.57,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ネロから連絡が来た
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.80,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,来週の礼拝の後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:35.10,Default,ron,0,0,0,,He's going to meet me at this\N mansion next week after mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.10,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,この屋敷で会うことになりそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.88,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Then the Vanetti family will be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.88,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,これでバネッチィファミリーはお前のものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.22,Default,fra,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.90,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.90,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:12.47,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Damn, I couldn't finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:12.47,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,くそ 討ち漏らした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.72,Default,av,0,0,0,,Were you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.72,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,傷は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.93,Default,vol,0,0,0,,Tigre's gonna laugh at me, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.93,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,ティグレに笑われちまうな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.62,Default,av,0,0,0,,We'll need to go somewhere to stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.62,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,どこかで止血しないとなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.65,Default,vol,0,0,0,,The bleeding isn't stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.65,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,血が止まねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:31.29,Default,vol,0,0,0,,By the way, we need to tell Nero about—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:31.29,通用720日文-ja,vol,0,0,0,,そう言や ネロにはこのこと...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.09,Default,av,0,0,0,,Leave Nero to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.09,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ネロのことは任せておけ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:44.51,Default,fra,0,0,0,,It's Volpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:44.51,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,ボルペだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:49.27,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Calm down, Nero wouldn't do something like—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:49.27,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,冷静になれ ネロはこんなことをする奴...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.47,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.47,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,ふさげるな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.93,Default,fra,0,0,0,,He almost killed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.93,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,俺達は 殺されかけたんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.81,Default,fra,0,0,0,,And Ronaldo, of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.81,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,よりによって ロナルドが...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.58,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Which means now, it's kill or be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.58,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,こうなったら やるか やられるかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:45.63,Default,fra,0,0,0,,I can't live this way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:45.63,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,もう 嫌だ こんな生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.76,Default,fra,0,0,0,,How much longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.76,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,何時まで...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.51,Default,ron,0,0,0,,He's just rattling your chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.51,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ただの挑発だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.49,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Don Vanetti's in this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.49,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,この屋敷にはドン ヴァネッティもいる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.33,Default,ron,0,0,0,,He can't do anything serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.33,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,大したことは出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.42,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Let's leave the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.42,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,町を出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.62,Default,fra,0,0,0,,If we go to the Galassias in Chicago—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.62,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,シカゴのガラッシアの所に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.22,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Don't act like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.22,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,甘えてんじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.37,Default,ron,0,0,0,,I'll work something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.37,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,おれが何とかしてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:11.06,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Have yourself a nice nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:11.06,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,今 ゆっくり休め
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.56,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.56,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.65,Default,ron,0,0,0,,I want to talk to Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.65,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ネロと話し合いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.86,Default,ron,0,0,0,,That's what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.86,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,お前が望んていた事だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.63,Default,ron,0,0,0,,I'll hear him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.63,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,願いを聞いてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.70,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Now, after everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.70,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,今更そんなこと?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:45.13,Default,ron,0,0,0,,At this rate, Frate will be killed by Nero,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:45.13,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,このままいけば フラテはネロにやられ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.62,Default,ron,0,0,0,,and the family will be crushed by the Galassias.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.62,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ファミリーはガラッシアに潰されつ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.99,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Nero will die as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.99,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ネロの命も
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:53.98,Default,ron,0,0,0,,and so will our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:53.98,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,そして 俺とお前の子も
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.81,Default,ron,0,0,0,,But I can save them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.81,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,だが 俺なら救ってやれる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:02.03,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Nero, Frate, the whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:02.03,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ネロもフラテも ファミリーも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.82,Default,ron,0,0,0,,You haven't told them about the baby yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.82,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,子供のことはまだ話していないんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.10,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Tell Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.10,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ネロに伝えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.76,Default,ron,0,0,0,,This baby is our hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.76,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,この子こそ 希望だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:14.85,Default,ron,0,0,0,,The symbol of reconciliation\N between Galassias and Vanettis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:14.85,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ガラッシアとヴァネッティとの和解の象徴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:20.00,Default,ron,0,0,0,,This child will restore everything to its proper path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:20.00,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,この子が 全てをあるべき道に戻してくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:35.53,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You've been working hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:35.53,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ご活躍だな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:39.76,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You really are the guy destined to\N become the don of the Vanettis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:39.76,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,やっぱりお前はヴァネッティのドンになる男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.22,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I'll help you however you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.22,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,いくらでも協力するぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:49.49,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Keep it up to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:49.49,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,最後の仕上げまできっちりな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:53.73,Default,nero,0,0,0,,How many of ours have been killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:53.73,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,一体何人殺された
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.81,Default,nero,0,0,0,,And how many have we killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.81,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,何人殺したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.88,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We all used to be part of the same family...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.88,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,元は同じファミリーだったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:00.78,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:00.78,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.36,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Phone call for you, from Fio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.36,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,電話だ フィオから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.64,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Fio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.64,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,フィオ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.54,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Brother, there's something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.54,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,兄さん 話があるの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.14,Default,ron,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.14,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.69,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Nero's sent a messenger.\N Should I let him through?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.69,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ネロの使いの者が来た 通していいか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.10,Default,ron,0,0,0,,You pat him down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.10,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ボディーチェックは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.55,Default,gan,0,0,0,,He's clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.55,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.21,Default,av,0,0,0,,These are for you, Fio, from Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.21,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,フィオさんにネロから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.31,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Where's my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.31,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,兄さんは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.27,Default,av,0,0,0,,He said he'd be a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.27,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,少し遅れるそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.23,Default,fio,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.23,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:49.97,Default,ron,0,0,0,,You think he'll really come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:49.97,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,本当に来るんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:50.95,Default,av,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:50.95,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,勿論
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.93,Default,av,0,0,0,,He said he'd just be an hour late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.93,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,遅れると言っても 一時間程度です
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.59,Default,ron,0,0,0,,I'm determined to talk to him this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.59,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,この際 腹を割って話したい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.71,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Just me, Nero, and Fio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.71,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,俺とネロとフィオの三人だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:03.47,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yes, that's what Nero wants as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:03.47,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ええ ネロもそのつもりです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.24,Default,av,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.24,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.83,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.83,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,用心の為だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.62,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.62,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.83,Default,ron,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.83,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,きっと上手くいくさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.88,Default,fio,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.88,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,兄さんを殺すの?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:38.41,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Vanetti's only option is to\N become a puppet to the Galassias.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:38.41,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ヴァネッティはガラッシアの人形になるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.88,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Frate understands that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.88,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,フラテにはそれが分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.16,Default,ron,0,0,0,,But Nero...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.16,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,しかし ネロは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:48.37,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Don't you worry. It'll all—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:48.37,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,心配するな すぐ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.38,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Fio...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.38,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,フィオ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.62,Default,fio,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.62,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.73,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Damn Vanettis...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.73,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,ヴァ...ヴァネッティめ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:18.01,Default,fio,0,0,0,,It was the only way to protect Frate...\N to protect my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:18.01,通用720日文-ja,fio,0,0,0,,フラテを 家族を守るには こうするしか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.28,Default,ron,0,0,0,,Curse y—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.28,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,呪われ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.60,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Buona notte.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.60,720通用注釋-ja,gan,0,0,0,,意大利語:晚安的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.60,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ボウナ ノッテ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.12,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Frate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.12,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どうした フラテ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.65,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You're looking ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.65,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,顔色が悪いぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.09,Default,nero,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna stay cooped up in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.09,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,何時まで そこに閉じこもってる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.09,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.09,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,全部終わったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:02.75,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Go out to the country for some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:02.75,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,暫く田舎の空気でも吸ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:07.71,Default,fra,0,0,0,,I'm never coming back to this house, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:07.71,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,もう 俺がこの家に帰ってくることはないんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:13.44,Default,fra,0,0,0,,I never missed mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:13.44,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,俺は一度も礼拝を休まなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:17.41,Default,fra,0,0,0,,You always did whatever you wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:17.41,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,兄さんは何時も勝手なことばかりしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.23,Default,fra,0,0,0,,And yet, you're the one Dad cared about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.23,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,なのに 父さんが可愛がったのは兄さんだった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:26.08,Default,fra,0,0,0,,I always envied you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:26.08,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,俺はずっと 兄さんが羨ましかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.91,Default,fra,0,0,0,,Dad acknowledged you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.91,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,父さんに認められて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.91,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Dad loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.91,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,父さんはお前を愛してた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:36.88,Default,fra,0,0,0,,I don't want to be loved! I want to be acknowledged!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:36.88,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,俺は愛されたいんじゃあい 認められたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.99,Default,av,0,0,0,,What a load of nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.99,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,迷惑な話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:07.28,Default,av,0,0,0,,How many people did you drag into your little brothers' feud?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:07.28,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,お前達の兄弟喧嘩に 一体何人付き合わされたんだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:12.20,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why don't you just put an end to it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:12.20,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,もういい加減 終わりにしたらどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:25.66,Default,fra,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:28.56,通用720日文-ja,fra,0,0,0,,俺は怖がってなんて...自分で示す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:28.09,Default,fra,0,0,0,,I'll prove it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.64,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Frate, don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.64,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,フラテ 止めろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.28,Default_Italics,ron,0,0,0,,Do it, Frate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.28,通用720日文-ja,ron,0,0,0,,やれ フラテ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:15.23,Default,av,0,0,0,,Frate is the one who killed Ronaldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:15.23,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ロナルドを殺したのはフラテです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:19.90,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,だからネロは ガラッシアへの忠誠を示す為 弟を手にかけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:21.94,Default,av,0,0,0,,That's why Nero killed his brother,\N to prove his loyalty to the Galassias.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.94,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,弟を手に掛けた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:07.20,Default,av,0,0,0,,Nero...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:07.20,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:10.16,Default,av,0,0,0,,Starting today, I'll be your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:10.16,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,今日からは俺が兄弟だ
